&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    京都・高瀬川沿いの夕暮れ時の桜。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Dusk" /><summary type="html">Cherry blossoms at dusk, along the Takasegawa River in Kyoto.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R07298.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R07298.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Pond at Ryoanji・龍安寺の池</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220409/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Pond at Ryoanji・龍安寺の池" /><published>2022-04-09T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-04-09T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/ryoanji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220409/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
